  "title": "Warm Gooey Tunisian Meal-Prep Bake",
  "description": "A floral, gooey, meal-prep Tunisian dish featuring glace cherry and shio-koji-cure, with a focus on satvik-friendly ingredients. Perfect for a weeknight dinner or meal prep.",
